title: crux
pid: 03f81db9-c8ce-40db-8109-569e06746369
body: |2-
  Containment can be replaced with 'show this relationship',
  and the relationship label can be a list of strings,
  perhaps often a singleton character like & or /.
  It would be smart to collect the set of such labels one had used,
  and classify them, for future use.
